    • RTreePolicy

      public RTreePolicy​(@NotNull @NotNull PolicyRight policyRight, @NotNull @NotNull java.lang.String... namespaceDirectories)
      Constructor for the RTreePolicy class.
      Parameters:
      policyRight - The access right of the policy (READ / WRITE).
      namespaceDirectories - Strings expressing the directory of the namespace. E.g. "A", "B" ==> RTreePolicy expressing access to the namespace "A/B", according to the policy right. At least one String should be provided.

    • coversRTreePolicy

      public boolean coversRTreePolicy​(@NotNull @NotNull RTreePolicy otherRTreePolicy)
      Method to check if this RTreePolicy object covers the RTree policy of another RTreePolicy object. This is the case if the following criteria are met: - The PolicyRight of this RTreePolicy object is at least as expressive as the PolicyRight of the other RTreePolicy object, with WRITE > READ. - The namespace directory of this object is either a parent namespace directory of the provided object, or is the same namespace directory as the namespace directory of the provided object.
      Parameters:
      otherRTreePolicy - The other RTreePolicy object.
      Returns:
      True if this RTreePolicy object covers the RTree policy of the provided RTreePolicy object; false otherwise.
